snippet.title: God of War III Remastered - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/god-of-war/?emcid=or-1s-412983

In beautiful 1080p targeting 60FPS, experience God of War III Remastered on PlayStation 4. Relive the legend, or experience one hell of a ride. 

Get creative with the brand new photo mode and share your epic images with http://www.twitter.com/sonysantamonica

http://godofwar.playstation.com/


Rated Mature: Blood and Gore, Intense Violence, Nudity, Strong Language, Strong Sexual Content
